sprites

Class Vacuum

  • java.lang.Object
    • sprites.Sprite
      • sprites.Vacuum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Moveable

    public class Vacuum
extends Sprite
implements Moveable
    A representation of a movaeble vacuum for the vacuum game. At creation, it initializes its capacity, fullness and sets the surface under it to a clean hallway. When asked to clean, it is only able to do so when it is not full.
